    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the risotto is cooking, line a baking tray with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> remaining bacon</strong> to the tray and drizzle over <strong>half</strong> your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> (save the rest for later!) and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the bacon is well coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
