        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim the woody ends off your <strong>asparagus</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>asparagus</strong> into bite-sized pieces and add it to the tray with the bacon with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>When the risotto has 10 min remaining, put the tray in the oven and cook for 8-10 min or until the bacon is crispy and the asparagus is tender – this is your <strong>balsamic glazed bacon</strong> <strong>&</strong> <strong>roasted asparagus</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
