    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>salad </strong>and <strong>chopped tomato</strong> in a bowl with the <strong>remaining balsamic vinegar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> – this is your <strong>salad</strong></p>",
