    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the risotto<strong> </strong>is ready, stir through 3/4<strong> </strong>of your <strong>grated Italian cheese </strong>and a generous grind of <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your <strong>bacon risotto</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> balsamic glazed bacon & roasted asparagus </strong>with the <strong>remaining grated Italian cheese </strong>– this is your<strong> balsamic glazed bacon & asparagus topping</strong></p>",
